  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ONE MATCH. EVERY WAY TO LIVE IT.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Motion Soccer is the VR football simulator where you do much more than simply play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step onto the pitch in <strong>first person</strong>, coach from the sideline or grab the whistle and <strong>referee the match yourself</strong>. Play full <strong>11v11</strong> matches with clubs and national teams inspired by real football and experience the same game from completely different roles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🟨 <strong>BE THE REFEREE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Call fouls, show cards and control the flow of the match directly from the pitch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/361fe0fb1f5fef8c5d2271c689fa820d.poster.avif?t=1773311575\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/361fe0fb1f5fef8c5d2271c689fa820d.webm?t=1773311575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/361fe0fb1f5fef8c5d2271c689fa820d.mp4?t=1773311575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚽ <strong>PLAY IN FIRST PERSON</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel every pass, dribble and shot from inside the action. Use <strong>Standard Control</strong> with sticks or go deeper with <strong>Expert Control</strong>, moving your hands like your feet to strike the ball with greater immersion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/e41baf2fbadcddd29b28eff43a461409.poster.avif?t=1773311575\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/e41baf2fbadcddd29b28eff43a461409.webm?t=1773311575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/e41baf2fbadcddd29b28eff43a461409.mp4?t=1773311575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 <strong>COACH FROM THE SIDELINE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the match in <strong>first person</strong> from the bench or control the strategy using the tactical view. Adjust formations and make real-time decisions to change the course of the match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/2b8594887e679b9a13ff195327ff51d9.poster.avif?t=1773311575\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/2b8594887e679b9a13ff195327ff51d9.webm?t=1773311575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/2b8594887e679b9a13ff195327ff51d9.mp4?t=1773311575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 <strong>PLAY A FULL SEASON</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your club or national team and compete in <strong>league and cup</strong>, managing team morale and facing press conferences throughout the season.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 <strong>MULTIPLAYER UP TO 11v11</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play online from <strong>1v1 up to full 11v11 matches</strong>, combining human players and AI. Each participant can join the same match from a different perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>One match. Every way to live it.</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ONE MATCH. EVERY WAY TO LIVE IT.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Motion Soccer is the VR football simulator where you do much more than simply play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step onto the pitch in <strong>first person</strong>, coach from the sideline or grab the whistle and <strong>referee the match yourself</strong>. Play full <strong>11v11</strong> matches with clubs and national teams inspired by real football and experience the same game from completely different roles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🟨 <strong>BE THE REFEREE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Call fouls, show cards and control the flow of the match directly from the pitch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/361fe0fb1f5fef8c5d2271c689fa820d.poster.avif?t=1773311575\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/361fe0fb1f5fef8c5d2271c689fa820d.webm?t=1773311575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/361fe0fb1f5fef8c5d2271c689fa820d.mp4?t=1773311575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚽ <strong>PLAY IN FIRST PERSON</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel every pass, dribble and shot from inside the action. Use <strong>Standard Control</strong> with sticks or go deeper with <strong>Expert Control</strong>, moving your hands like your feet to strike the ball with greater immersion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/e41baf2fbadcddd29b28eff43a461409.poster.avif?t=1773311575\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/e41baf2fbadcddd29b28eff43a461409.webm?t=1773311575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/e41baf2fbadcddd29b28eff43a461409.mp4?t=1773311575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 <strong>COACH FROM THE SIDELINE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the match in <strong>first person</strong> from the bench or control the strategy using the tactical view. Adjust formations and make real-time decisions to change the course of the match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/2b8594887e679b9a13ff195327ff51d9.poster.avif?t=1773311575\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/2b8594887e679b9a13ff195327ff51d9.webm?t=1773311575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137350/extras/2b8594887e679b9a13ff195327ff51d9.mp4?t=1773311575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 <strong>PLAY A FULL SEASON</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your club or national team and compete in <strong>league and cup</strong>, managing team morale and facing press conferences throughout the season.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 <strong>MULTIPLAYER UP TO 11v11</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play online from <strong>1v1 up to full 11v11 matches</strong>, combining human players and AI. Each participant can join the same match from a different perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>One match. Every way to live it.</strong></p>",
